Details_explanation: Rockstud flat sandals. Black leather. Cage effect on the top, with golden studs. Adjustable ankle strap. Square ends. Leather insole. Made in Italy. Size: 38. Note: Signs of wear on the outer soles, Slight scratch at the right end. Packaging: dust bag.

2017. Grayish pink Sac de Jour handbag with an embossed crocodile pattern. Silver colored brass fittings. Padlock and its keys. Smooth leather interior in the same tone. Slight small marks at the bottom inside, light marks of friction at the top inside, slightly patinated handles.
